name: Prozac
sideEffects: weakness, anxiety, drowsiness, tremor, diarrhea, dyspepsia, nausea, nervousness, insomnia, headache, xerostomia, decreased libido, anorexia, and decreased appetite. Other side effects include bulimia nervosa, dizziness, skin rash, and diaphoresis
